title: Acoustic & Slide Guitar Lessons Pack
description:
Some of the acoustic and slide guitar lessons that I've collected over time and it seemed a shame not to share it with other people. Some of these are my own dvd rips, others are from other sources.



- A Guitarist's Guide to Better Practicing

- Acoustic Fingerstyle with Rick Ruskin

- Acoustic Guitar Slide Basics

- Guitar World - Acoustic Rock Guitar

- Hotlicks Lesson Warren Haynes 2 - Acoustic Slide Guitar

- Lick Library - Rock Slide Guitar

- Lick Library - The Mechanics of Acoustic Guitar (disk 1&2)

- Woody Mann - Art Of Acoustic Blues Guitar - Early Roots

- Woody Mann - Art Of Acoustic Blues Guitar - Handful Of Riffs





As always, enjoy & seed!
